{"tid":306314,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【儲錢有獎】三藩市府派錢鼓勵市民儲 (17:53)","createTime":"2017-07-02T12:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T05:19:13.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de560c8cd599e54eb0dbfe70999703303afaf09f","tid":306314,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=N0f95%2Bvow%2B00TehFV0DM%2Ff755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fb2d7ee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】「6個月儲到120蚊，政府補貼你60蚊」！你無睇錯，美國三藩市政府為鼓勵市民儲錢，實行「你儲錢，我派錢」。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，三藩市正在招募1000人參加一項名為Saverlife的活動。按照該活動的規定，參與者如果在6個月裡每月存儲20美元，那麼市政府會提供給他們60美元。<br />\n<br />\n參與者將自己的銀行帳戶通過電子方式連接到Saverlife，這樣他們的儲蓄活動就可以被監控。他們每月能獲得10美元的獎勵，在連續6個月的持續儲蓄中可以獲得60美元的獎勵。<br />\n<br />\nSaverlife的獎勵金來自私人捐贈者和企業贊助商的資助，參與該項目的人每周會收到財務指導建議。<br />\n<br />\n調查顯示，將近一半的美國人缺乏足夠的現金儲蓄，他們甚至拿不出400美元用於緊急費用支出。<br />\n<br />\n總部在華盛頓特區的智庫Urban Institute最近的一項研究發現，三藩市是美國居住成本最為昂貴的城市之一，每人每年在三藩市市要花110,357美元。這反映了一種美國全國性的趨勢，大約47%的三藩市家庭在經濟上不牢靠，這意味著他們的儲蓄不足2,000美元。<br />\n<br />\n根據Urban Institute的數據，三藩市許多家庭的金融不穩定最終導致市政府和納稅人每年損失2,400萬到5,400萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170702/20170702175350fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170702%2F20170702175350fi.html&d=N0f95%2Bvow%2B00TehFV0DM%2Ff755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ed46369d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170702/20170702175350fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"eae4d0d5c346357113561bf0bf49ebc90a00928a","tid":306314,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15241a2d042fce43ec44edc62cbdb34cf0269b10","tid":306314,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"香港政府幾時考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59e8fba00b0a867bb2e1732eb869a7a3c215de3","tid":306314,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港政府幾時考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港有ibond 入10000比400你"},{"pid":"7c0c93fdb7e6f4662f4afebb3de19027266073dd","tid":306314,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港政府幾時考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港有ibond 入10000比400你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今年ibond 都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17b50ea55c832b2ed7d62575664de2ffb210ab2","tid":306314,"uid":35815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0822d7b99ab48670994516f6633be39a08ad574e","tid":306314,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:39:13.000Z","msg":"香港人除左食仲有咩錢好使呀<br />\n住就有錢都買唔起<br />\n玩又冇野好玩<br />\n衣又冇地方擺<br />\n行又唔係貴又唔係周圍去"},{"pid":"9e732087ef5d7ad4eaa73c0842acec901f31e4ee","tid":306314,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"每人每年在三藩市市要花110,357美元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁誇張？"},{"pid":"149e5d67488c6dfdcca96af0a3f542937224d8bd","tid":306314,"uid":92023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每人每年在三藩市市要花110,357美元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁誇張？</blockquote><br />\n因為啲租好撚貴"},{"pid":"c1b9d96b90e3ec7918ceb1a3b5344e67c326a042","tid":306314,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港問題係戶口係太多錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會鼓勵市民儲錢<br />\n相反應該鼓勵市民洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人係有錢消費又有儲蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02db8a2023bef5331828d7289c99e53f2215faa","tid":306314,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2699782da68289f5ebe7de2b382b888e90cc2d","tid":306314,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每人每年在三藩市市要花110,357美元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁誇張？</blockquote><br />\n因為啲租好撚貴</blockquote><br />\n每人用成八十幾萬港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地人工幾錢"}]}